title: 5A Girl's Preseason All State - Second Team
text:
5A Girl's Preseason All State - Second Team Luke Feddersen IowaPreps.com Editor 
One of the most popular features on Iowa Preps is our preseason girls All State basketball teams. We take an in-depth look at Class 5A and name our second team All State. See which of the elite athletes around Iowa made the cut as we take a look towards a winter full of hoops! 
Class 5A Girl's Preseason All State - Second Team Rachel Zingg, Ottumwa
